\operatorname{\rm sinc}(x)=\dfrac{\sin(\pi x)}{\pi x}
\varphi_n(x)
\int_{-\infty}^\infty \varphi_n(x) \varphi_m(x) \mathrm{d} x = \delta_{n,m}
c_n = \int_{-\infty}^\infty \varphi_n(x) \operatorname{\mathrm{sinc}}(x) \mathrm{d} x
c_{2m+1} = 0
    \operatorname{\mathrm{sinc}}(x) = \sum_{n=0}^\infty c_n \varphi_n(x) 
